videos.description: Devon Dotson easily gets to the bucket and scores, forcing a Kansas State timeout and getting the crowd on their feet.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dotson's layup forces an early Kansas State timeout) 2020/01/21

videos.headline: Dotson's layup forces an early Kansas State timeout

videos.description: Kansas gets out in transition and Ochai Agbaji follows the Devon Dotson miss with a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Agbaji flushes putback dunk

videos.description: Devon Dotson is fouled and is still able to put in the tough reverse layup.

videos.headline: Dotson's gets the acrobatic layup to fall

videos.description: Bill Self says his Kansas players were "in the wrong" for their role in the melee with Kansas State, and explains the referee's ruling of ejecting the entire team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Self calls brawl an embarrassment) 2020/01/21

videos.headline: Self calls brawl an embarrassment

videos.description: Dick Vitale says there is no excuse for the brawl at the end of the Kansas State vs. Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Dickie V: KSU-Kansas brawl was ‘sickening’) 2020/1/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dickie V: KSU-Kansas brawl was 'sickening'

videos.description: Kansas State coach Bruce Weber says he was disappointed in the brawl that broke out vs. Kansas, but told his players to learn from what transpired.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Weber told players to learn lesson from fight) 2020/01/21
